dct_title_s: Carte administrative régions, provinces, préfectures et communes [cartographic material] : [Maroc] / Agence nationale de la conservation fonciére du cadastre et de la cartographie, Division de la cartographie.
dct_description_sm: Includes legend of administrative boundaries, legend of wilayas, 2 location maps, and 4 inset maps. Legend of administrative boundaries includes of regions, provinces or prefectures, towns, and districts. Panel title.
